Say 'This is a Mixed-Mode Message'
sAy 'This is an example of a literal that is continued on',
    'another line using a comma at the end of the first line.'
saY "This is two"          'quoted literals'
SAY "These two"  ||      'literals contain the || to eliminate blank'
say 'This is an example'; say 'of two statements on one line'
